Package net.ashwork.upvote.domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReputationEntry<USER,REPUTATION,TIME>
    A helper that specifies that a particular object entry is a user's reputation made up of the user whose reputation is being determined, the reputation of the user, and the time that the determination was made.
    TimestampEntry<TIME>
    A helper that specifies that a particular object entry has a timestamp with some type.
    UserEntry<USER>
    A helper that specifies that a particular object entry has a user with some type.
    VoteEntry<USER,ITEM,VOTE,TIME>
    A helper that specifies that a particular object entry is a vote made up of the user who made the vote, the item being voted on, the vote the user cast, and the time the vote was made.
